### Test Candlestick Pattern Detection with Sample Data
GET http://localhost:8000/candlestick/test/

###

### Analyze Candlestick Patterns for AAPL (Apple)
GET http://localhost:8000/candlestick/patterns/AAPL/?period=1mo&interval=1d

###

### Analyze Candlestick Patterns for GOOGL (Google) - 3 months daily
GET http://localhost:8000/candlestick/patterns/GOOGL/?period=3mo&interval=1d

###

### Analyze Candlestick Patterns for MSFT (Microsoft) - 1 week hourly
GET http://localhost:8000/candlestick/patterns/MSFT/?period=1wk&interval=1h

###

### Analyze Candlestick Patterns with date range
GET http://localhost:8000/candlestick/patterns/TSLA/?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-12-31

###

### Analyze Candlestick Patterns - hourly data only from database
GET http://localhost:8000/candlestick/patterns/AAPL/?is_hourly=true

